y: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">【功能主治】&nbsp;白藜芦醇是一种天然的抗氧化剂，可降低血液粘稠度，抑制血小板凝结和血管舒张，保持血液畅通，可预防癌症的发生及发展，具有抗动脉粥样硬化和冠心病，缺血性心脏病，高血脂的防治作用。　抑制肿瘤的作用还具有雌激素样作用，可用于治疗乳腺癌等疾病。&nbsp;规格与物理性质　</span></p>\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">【规&nbsp;格】&nbsp;50%&nbsp;90%&nbsp;98%</span></p>\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">【物理性质】&nbsp;无味、白色晶体粉末；难溶于水，易溶于乙醇，丙酮等有机溶剂。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">功能主治</span><br />\n	<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">【功能主治】&nbsp;白藜芦醇是一种天然的抗氧化剂，可降低血液粘稠度，抑制血小板凝结和血管舒张，保持血液畅通，可预防癌症的发生及发展，具有抗动脉粥样硬化和冠心病，缺血性心脏病，高血脂的防治作用。　抑制肿瘤的作用还具有雌激素样作用，可用于治疗乳腺癌。</span></p>\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">临床应用与药理作用　</span></p>\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">【临床应用】：用于急性黄疸型传染性肝炎，血瘀闭经，风湿型关节痛、筋骨痛、砂淋、血淋、气管炎、湿热型　胆囊结石病；用于血胆固醇和甘油三酯过高；用于抗氧化、延缓衰老,是抗肿瘤药物开发的原料。</span></p>\n', '600.00', null, '6.0', '0', 'upload/pic/2017053114361796.jpg', '2017-05-31 14:05:20');
INSERT INTO `companyproduct` VALUES ('b3033833a5508e6584ea815140644ea6b3ae6b6d', 'c1089f14f09f3ee9d5cb2be62a4fcd8a275423c2', '当归提取物', '<p>\n	<strong><font color=\"#313230\" face=\"微软雅黑\" size=\"3\">产品规格：</font></strong><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>蒿本内酯1%，阿魏酸0.1%，1%</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">检测方法：</strong><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; HPLC</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">来源:</strong><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">本品为伞形科植物当归Angelica sinensis(oliv.) Diels的干燥根。<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">性状:</strong><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>本品为黄色粉末或颗粒，有浓郁香气，味甘、辛、微苦。<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">制剂:</strong><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>浸膏粉，颗粒剂。</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">性味归经:</strong><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">味甘、辛、苦。性温。归肝、心、脾经。</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">功能主治:</strong><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">补血，活血，调经止痛，润燥滑肠。主治血虚诸证，月经不调，经闭，痛经，癥瘕结聚，崩漏，虚寒腹痛，痿痹，肌肤麻木，肠燥便难，赤痢缓重，痈疽疮疡，跌扑损伤。<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">古籍论述:</strong><span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">《别录》：（当归）&ldquo;温中止痛，除客血内塞，中风痉，汗不出，湿痹，中恶客气，虚冷，补五脏，生肌肉。&rdquo;</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 《本经》：（当归）&ldquo;主咳逆止气，温疟寒热洗在皮肤中，妇人漏下，绝子，诸恶疮疡金疮，煮饮之。&rdquo;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 《药性论》：（当归）&ldquo;止呕逆，虚劳寒热，破宿血，主女子崩中，下肠胃冷，补诸不足，止痢腹痛。&rdquo;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 《医学启源》：（当归）&ldquo;能和血补血。《主治秘要》云:其用有三:心经药一也，和血二也，治诸病夜其三也。&rdquo;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 《本草再新》：（当归）&ldquo;治浑身肿胀，血脉不和，阴分不足，兼能安生胎，堕死胎。&rdquo;</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">古代临床应用</strong><br />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1）汉代用于治疗虚寒腹痛、瘀血作痛、跌打损伤、痹痛麻木。当归补血活血，善止血虚血瘀之痛，且有散寒功效。如《金匮要略》之当归生姜羊肉汤、《千金翼方》之当归建中汤。<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2）《医学启源》云：&ldquo;血壅而不流则痛，当归身辛温以散之，使气血各有所归。&rdquo;故当归具活血消肿，祛瘀止痛之功，适用于瘀血疼痛，跌打损伤，风湿痹痛等证。<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3）晋代以当归补血活血，能起到消肿止痛，排脓生肌的功效，故也为外科所常用。如在外科专著《刘涓子鬼遗方》中应用当归者，就达数十方之多。</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">现代研究<br />\n	化学成分</strong><br />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当归含挥发油（其中主要成分为蒿本内酯、当归酮、阿魏酸等）、非挥发成分、糖、氨基酸、磷脂类及微量元素等。<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">药理作用</strong><br />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.对血液与造血系统的影响</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当归是中医&ldquo;补血、活血&rdquo;要药，临床和实验研究显示较好疗效。当归水浸液给小鼠口服能显著促进红血蛋白和红细胞的生成。其抗贫血作用可能与所含的维生素B12、烟酸、亚叶酸及生物素、叶酸等成分有关。</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.对血压的影响</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当归能扩张外周血管，降低血管阻力，加速血流量。作用强度随剂量的加大而增强。</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3.降血脂及对动脉硬化的影响</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当归粉1.5g/kg口服对大白鼠及家兔实验性高血脂症有降血脂作用。含5%当归粉的食物及相当于此量的当归油及其他提取物，对实验性动脉硬化大白鼠的病变主动脉有一定保护作用。<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.对子宫的作用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当归是妇科圣药，除补血活血外当归含有兴奋和抑制子宫平滑肌的两种成分，具有&ldquo;双向性&rdquo;作用，抑制成分主要为挥发油。</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.其他</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当归对人体免疫功能有增强作用，有抗炎镇痛，镇静及抗氧化和清除自由基等作用。</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 当归用于治疗痛经，子宫脱垂，镇痛，缺血性中风，心律失常、血栓闭塞性脉管炎，动脉硬化，镰状细胞贫血等。</span></p>\n', '400.00', null, '8.0', '0', 'upload/pic/2017053114335861.jpg', '2017-05-31 14:05:03');
INSERT INTO `companyproduct` VALUES ('e84a7754f58891ed56f23b866eda99c869c01a14', 'e3e3e5d3ffa64bf51882fd19d5287b3da15c2844', '有机糙米', '<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	<img border=\"0\" src=\"http://www.yonghuinongye.com/uploadfile/201403/20140307103459853.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 糙米（Oryza sativa,spp.），是指除了外壳之外都保留的全谷粒，即含有皮层、糊粉层和胚芽的米。由于口感较粗，质地紧密，煮起来也比较费时，但是糙米的营养价值比精白米高，与全麦相比，糙米的蛋白质质量较好，主要是米精蛋白，氨基酸的组成比较完全。人体容易消化吸收，但赖氨酸含量较少，含有较多的脂肪和碳水化合物，短时间内可以为人体提供大量的热量。<br />\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; 本产品生产和加工过程中依照有机生产技术规程不使用化肥、农药、生长激素、化学添加剂、化学色素和防腐剂等化学物质，是一种真正源于自然、高营养、高品质的有机食品<br />\n	食用方法：<br />\n	１、糙米口感较粗，质地紧密煮起来也比较费时，煮前浸洗后可用凉水浸泡过夜，然后连浸泡水和糙米一起投入高压锅，煮半小时以上。由于糙米口感不好煮饭时可加10-50和糯米(粘米)即可</p>\n', '120.00', null, '1.0', '0', 'upload/pic/2017053115044435.jpg', '2017-05-31 15:05:48');
INSERT INTO `companyproduct` VALUES ('4f855a3b17835d00f361cc27a5d4ed69ca689b18', 'c21034d8e652113923ddab50944a22a14dfce98e', '2L姜汁醋', '<p>\n	100%纯粮酿造。</p>\n', '20.00', null, '8.0', '0', 'upload/pic/2017053114473744.jpg', '2017-05-31 14:05:43');
INSERT INTO `companyproduct` VALUES ('64947e43d46b97a581df148ac6c18b498388ba35', '31320f22ce19d976c93fd38166b535049cdca337', '陕西名酒朱鹮黑米酒银超月子酒', '<div>\n	建议零售价 &yen;288.00 产品类别 加饭酒</div>\n<div>\n	品牌 朱鹮<br />\n	商品条形码 69427907081</div>\n<div>\n	原产地 陕西<br />\n	生产许可证编号 sc11561072300569</div>\n<div>\n	原料与配料 糯米黄酒</div>\n<div>\n	特产 是<br />\n	保质期 5（年）</div>\n<div>\n	生产日期 20160521</div>\n<div>\n	生产厂家 陕西朱鹮酒业</div>\n', '288.00', null, '10.0', '0', 'upload/pic/2017053115254712.png', '2017-05-31 15:05:05');
INSERT INTO `companyproduct` VALUES ('6fb831c11bc002fb952163315e2479b45a5a3a85', 'c1089f14f09f3ee9d5cb2be62a4fcd8a275423c2', '穿心莲内酯', '<div class=\"Section0\">\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">【产品名称】</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">&nbsp;穿心莲内酯</span><br />\n		<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">【英文名称】</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">Andrographolide</span><br />\n		<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">【别&nbsp;名】</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">穿心莲乙素，雄茸内脂</span><br />\n		<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">【C&nbsp;A&nbsp;S&nbsp;号】</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">5508-58-7</span><br />\n		<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">【化学名称】</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">293H)-Furanone,&nbsp;3-[2-[decahydro-6-hydroxy-5-&nbsp;(hydroxy-methyl)-5,8a-dimethyl-2-methylene-1-naphthalenyl]&nbsp;ethylidene]dihydro-4-hydroxy-</span><br />\n		<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">【植物来源】</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">爵床科植物穿心莲Andrographis&nbsp;Paniculata(Burm.f)&nbsp;Ness的全草或叶。</span><br />\n		<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">【分&nbsp;子&nbsp;式】</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">&nbsp;C20H30O5;</span><br />\n		<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">【分&nbsp;子&nbsp;量】</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">&nbsp;350.44</span><br />\n		<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">【成分分类】</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">&nbsp;二萜内酯类</span><br />\n		<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">【执行标准】</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">WS-10001-(HD-0971)-2002</span><br />\n		<span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">【规　格】</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">穿心莲内酯含量99%</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">物理性质　</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;白色方棱形或片状结晶&nbsp;(乙醇或甲醇),&nbsp;无臭，味苦。在沸乙醇中溶解，在甲醇或乙醇中略溶，极微溶于氯仿，在水或乙醚中几乎不溶。熔点230～231℃,&nbsp;(&alpha;)17D&nbsp;-126.6&plusmn;2&deg;(冰醋酸)，[&alpha;]D&nbsp;&ndash;112.7&nbsp;(c,0.53,MeOH)，与碱性2％&nbsp;3,5－二硝基苯甲酸试剂，显紫红色，异羟肟酸铁反应呈阳性。密度(21℃)1.2317g/cm3。UV&lambda;EtOHmax&nbsp;nm&nbsp;(&epsilon;),&nbsp;223(12300);&nbsp;IRｖKBrmax&nbsp;cm-1:&nbsp;3448,&nbsp;3390～?279(OH),&nbsp;1828,&nbsp;1647,&nbsp;906&nbsp;(C=CH2),&nbsp;1727&nbsp;(&alpha;，&beta;-不饱和&gamma;-内酯),&nbsp;1672&nbsp;(共&nbsp;的C=C);&nbsp;13CNMR。</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">制备方法</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　　</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;穿心莲叶用95%乙醇浸泡，所得乙醇浸泡取液用活性炭脱色，脱色液蒸馏回收乙醇后的浓缩液静置得到粗晶品，粗晶加15倍量95%乙醇加热溶解，活性炭脱色，趁热过滤，静置重结晶，得淡黄色重结晶品，再经蒸馏水、氯仿、甲醇洗涤精制得到穿心莲内酯成品。对生药计，总收率1-1.5%。</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">药理作用</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　穿心莲内酯为天然植物穿心莲的主要有效成份，具有祛热解毒，消炎止痛之功效，对细菌性与病毒性上呼吸道感染及痢疾有特殊疗效，被誉为天然抗生素药物。本品为二萜类内酯化合物，均难溶于水，通常仅能口服给药。</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　　1.&nbsp;抗病原微生物作用　</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　　动物实验表明：穿心莲内酯及新穿心莲内酯均有抑制和延缓肺炎双球菌或溶血性乙型链球菌所引起的体温升高作用，但穿心莲内酯比新穿心莲内酯的作用较强。</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　　体外实验表明：穿心莲有一定抗HIV作用。</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　　2.&nbsp;解热作用　穿心莲内酯对家兔内毒素发热、肺炎球菌或溶血性链球菌所致发热有不同程度的解热作用。穿心莲甲、乙、丙、丁素对伤寒、副伤寒菌苗所致发热家兔或&nbsp;2,4-二硝基苯酚所致发热大白鼠的解热作用依次减弱。</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　　3.&nbsp;抗炎作用　穿心莲甲、乙、丙、丁素均有不同程度的抗炎作用，1g/kg&nbsp;灌服能抑制二甲苯或醋酸所致小鼠皮肤或腹腔毛细血管通透性的增高，减少&nbsp;Selye肉芽囊中巴豆油所致急性渗出液量，但对肉芽组织增生无明显影响。能抑制蛋清性大鼠脚肿的发展，但切除肾上腺后作用消失。丁素的抗炎作用最强，丙素、甲素、乙素次之。</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　　4.&nbsp;对机体免疫功能的影响　有报道认为，穿心莲可能对细胞免疫的某些环节有作用。其水煎剂在体外能提高人白细胞吞噬金黄色葡萄球菌的能力，口服穿心莲能使人对旧结核菌素所致的皮肤延缓型超敏反应增强。穿心莲制剂新炎得平（内含酯和酮），可提高小鼠血清溶菌酶水平，增强腹腔巨噬细胞和中性粒细胞的吞噬能力。连续给家兔或小鼠以穿心莲内酯磺化物，可明显增加外周血吞噬细胞对肺炎球菌或金黄色葡萄球菌的吞噬能力，穿心莲甲素注射液及喜炎平注射液亦能增强吞噬细胞功能。脱水穿心莲内酯琥珀酸半酯对&nbsp;2,4-二硝基氯苯所致小鼠迟发型超敏反应也有抑制作用。</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　　5&nbsp;抗生育作用　穿心莲有明显的中止妊娠作用。穿心莲口服能使小鼠避孕、孕兔流产。水煎剂腹腔注射对小鼠的着床、早孕、中孕、晚孕等不同时期均有显著的中止作用。肌注、皮下注射、灌服、腹腔注射、静脉注射及宫腔内注射均能产生抗早孕效果，其中以腹腔、静脉和宫内注射效果最好。宫腔内注射,用量既小,效果又佳。若将外源性孕酮或黄体生成素释放、激素（LH-RH）与穿心莲同时注射，则可防止流产，这提示，穿心莲可能有对抗体内孕酮的作用，从而引起流产。有人认为，穿心莲对体外培养的胎盘绒毛滋养层细胞的生长有一定的抑制作用。研究表明：穿心莲内酯的一些半合成衍生物亦有不同程度的抗早孕效果，脱水穿心莲内酯衍生物-穿-4对小鼠和大鼠均有良好的抗早孕作用，是值得进一步研究的一个避孕新药,该药对胎盘滋养叶细胞有显著的影响,可使胎盘绒毛萎缩、细胞数目减少,合体细胞和朗罕细胞消失、间质水肿出血。</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　　6.&nbsp;利胆保肝作用　穿心莲对大鼠有利胆作用，并可增加大鼠肝重，缩短环己巴比妥钠所致之睡眠时间。穿心莲内酯预先给药能对抗四氯化碳、D-半乳糖胺和乙酰胺基酚造成的肝毒性作用，能分别显著降低&nbsp;SGPT、SGOT、SALP、HTG&nbsp;水平。有报道指出，穿心莲的甲醇浸膏有毒性，可促进肝损伤大鼠的死亡。</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　　7.&nbsp;抗肿瘤作用　脱水穿心莲内酯琥珀酸半酯对W256移植性肿瘤有一定的抑制作用。脱水穿心莲内酯二琥珀酸半酯氢钾制成精氨酸复盐（简称穿琥氨酸），不论大、中、小剂量对肿瘤细胞均有抑制作用，且随剂量的增加而作用增强，抑瘤效果确实、稳定。体外实验证明：穿心莲对培养的乳腺癌细胞&nbsp;DNA&nbsp;合成有抑制作用。</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　　8.&nbsp;其他作用　炎琥宁及穿琥宁注射液有明显镇静作用，能缩短戊巴比妥钠对小鼠麻醉的潜伏期、延长麻醉时间，并能使阈下量的戊巴比妥钠引起麻醉。</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　　穿心莲内酯可增加肾上腺皮质功能，穿心莲甲、乙、丙、丁素在较大剂量时可使幼年小鼠胸腺萎缩。</span></strong></p>\n	<p class=\"p0\">\n		<strong style=\"line-height: 28px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold\">临床应用</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 14pt\">　　用于菌痢、钩端螺旋体病、脑膜炎、肺炎、增强肾上腺皮质功能、上呼吸道感染。针对临床上病毒感染急症的需求，将本品内酯结构中引入不同的亲水基团，增强其水溶性，提高疗效。由此已制成了多种穿心莲内酯的针剂，目前临床上应用较为广泛的穿琥宁针、炎琥宁针、莲必治针是本类的代表性药物，已被卫生部及国家中医药管理局列为急诊科必备药品之一。</span></strong></p>\n</div>\n', '300.00', null, '9.0', '0', 'upload/pic/2017053114372577.jpg', '2017-05-31 14:05:28');
INSERT INTO `companyproduct` VALUES ('bfb86141b325a0ef876820c964a3150867a433c3', 'c1089f14f09f3ee9d5cb2be62a4fcd8a275423c2', '西洋参皂甙', '<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	西洋参皂甙<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n	<strong>植物来源：</strong>本品为五加科植物西洋参的干燥根或根茎叶。均系栽培品，秋季采挖，洗净，晒干或低温干燥。</p>\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	<strong>性味归经：</strong>甘、微苦，凉。归心、肺、肾经。</p>\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	<strong>有效成分：</strong>含有多种生理活性成份，西洋参皂甙是西洋参中主要的有效成份，也是生理活性最显著的物质。西洋参（茎叶）皂甙与西洋参皂甙具有相似的生理活性。西洋参总皂甙除含有西洋参皂甙R1外，还含有人参皂甙的三大类群：人参二醇组皂甙包括Ra1、Ra2、Ra3、Rb1、Rb2、Rb3、Rc、Rd、Rg3、Rh2；人参三醇组皂甙包括Re、Rg1、Rg2、Rh1和齐墩果酸组R0。西洋参（茎叶）皂皂甙与西洋参（根部）皂甙的各种单体皂苷相同，其含量有一定差别。</p>\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	<strong>功 效：</strong>中医学认为西洋参皂甙有补气养阴，清热生津，清心安神，固本延寿之功效。现代医学研究表明西洋参皂甙具有增强机体的免疫功能，对中枢神经系统有镇静、催眠、抗惊厥作用，又能提高记忆力，用于治疗失眠、神经衰弱等症；对心肌缺血有改善作用，明显扩张冠状动脉，增加冠脉血流量，减少心肌耗氧量，对心律失常有对抗作用。降低血脂、血压作用，以及抗脂质过氧化作用。能延缓衰老，抗病毒以及促血凝、抗溶血、抗利尿和抗突变作用。</p>\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	<strong>主&nbsp;&nbsp;治：</strong>气虚阴亏，内热，咳喘痰血，虚热烦倦，消渴，口燥咽干。用于治疗冠心病、急性心肌梗塞、心肌缺血、心律失常、休克、高血脂、高血压等症</p>\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	<strong>规&nbsp;&nbsp;格：</strong>10%</p>\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/28px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(49,50,48); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\n	<strong>适用范围：</strong>制药</p>\n', '600.00', null, '9.0', '0', 'upload/pic/2017053114354236.jpg', '2017-05-31 14:05:46');
INSERT INTO `companyproduct` VALUES ('ddd07e2bb54bfa3259ef1bebcee9c2e1f21baddc', 'c21034d8e652113923ddab50944a22a14dfce98e', '馋嘴豆豉', '<p>\n	100%手工制作</p>\n', '10.00', null, '9.0', '0', 'upload/pic/2017053114510554.jpg', '2017-05-31 14:05:09');
INSERT INTO `companyproduct` VALUES ('9823c2bf0b4bddd683521bf1819d1863100b4fd4', 'c21034d8e652113923ddab50944a22a14dfce98e', '黑米口服醋', '<div>\n	黑米醋是高粱发酵酿造而成的，富含多种矿物质和多种氨基酸。经常适量地饮用黑米醋有降低血脂，降低血液粘度的作用。</div>\n', '25.00', null, '9.0', '0', 'upload/pic/2017053114522832.jpg', '2017-05-31 14:05:33');
