INSERT INTO `companyproduct` VALUES ('f1b0146a919d2817e9ef97396a0513a6eef03965', 'e3e3e5d3ffa64bf51882fd19d5287b3da15c2844', '盒装有机黑米2000克', '<p>\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在洋县具有三千多年的种植历史，自古就有&ldquo;月米&rdquo;、&ldquo;长寿米&rdquo;、&ldquo;米中之王&rdquo;等美称。该产品以有机种植基地种植的黒谷为原料，采用传统和现代工艺相结合加工精致而成，产品具有色泽紫黑光亮、手感光滑细腻、米香独特、嘴嚼感强的特点。自西汉汉武帝到清朝末年，洋县黑米均是向帝王仅供的贡米。常食洋县黑米，具有滋阴补肾、益气强身、明目活血的作用。</span></p>\n', '120.00', null, '1.0', '0', 'upload/pic/2017053115085322.jpg', '2017-05-31 15:05:56');
INSERT INTO `companyproduct` VALUES ('6e711178e20cd05e5cfda8e1f300a2a143473c52', 'e3e3e5d3ffa64bf51882fd19d5287b3da15c2844', '盒装有机五彩米1千克', '<p>\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (黑、红、黄、绿、紫)五色米又称五彩稻米产于中国黑米、红米渊源地， 世界珍奇朱鹮栖息地&mdash;陕西洋县五彩米，纯天然色泽，糙米营养成份保留完整，易糊化，口感好。堪称米中&ldquo;五珍&rdquo;。随着绿色有机产业的发展，永辉农业公司以独特的生态环境，大力发展有机五彩米为主的生态米业生产，不断满足人对特种米的需求，满足人们对高质量生活健康的追求。</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">食用方法：</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">１、煮粥，米水比例1：6左右，用清水淘洗1&mdash;2次，加水浸泡半小时，用文火煮1小时左右或在高压锅内煮40分钟左右即食。如白米，应先下五彩香米，水开后再下白米即可。</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">２、配以红枣、枸杞、百合、核桃仁、薏米仁，花生、桂圆、莲籽、冰糖等做八宝粥或米饭，营养更佳，早、晚吃一小碗，连吃2-3个月，体质明显增强。</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">３、黑糯米配以适量蜂蜜，核桃仁，黑芝麻做成黑米健脑粥，温热服食，补脑益气，补脑健肾。</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">４、可将原料磨成粉，加如食糖等原料，制作汤圆，糕点，沙琪玛等食品。</span><br style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\n	<span style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">５、将五彩香米加工发酵，酿成黑米酒，红香米酒、绿香米酒、黄香米酒、黑米啤酒、黑米酱油、黑米醋、黑米可乐等饮料，色泽鲜艳，香气幽人。</span></p>\n', '120.00', null, '1.0', '0', 'upload/pic/2017053115082043.jpg', '2017-05-31 15:05:24');
